{"tid":2312962,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"柯震東好命有富爸爸關照 獨居3千萬豪宅似Showroom","createTime":"2020-12-05T11:58:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-05T12:31:21.000Z","uid":212249,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"438211b52f7b0c2564f783fe7ec344ab2c245e3b","tid":2312962,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T11:58:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/my2a12IOnPxvb-_CEDaM9OUnQis=/720x405/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2R3RYKRE4FENRKSXI3D44M4FUQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fmy2a12IOnPxvb-_CEDaM9OUnQis%3D%2F720x405%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2R3RYKRE4FENRKSXI3D44M4FUQ.jpg&h=939aa092&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n台灣男星柯震東因在大陸涉吸毒遭封殺多年，歷經事業低潮，最終由柯爸爸出手，早前豪擲1,800萬港元購回《打噴嚏》大陸版權，電影封塵6年重見天日，但又遇上武漢肺炎，票房強差人意，但無礙其重新出發的心，近來更進軍KOL行列，昨日在開設的YouTube頻度大方公開自家台北東區豪宅，環境寬敞，裝潢簡約，設有私人影院，還有一間裝滿漫威、星球大戰、DC等動漫珍藏密室，擺滿各式各樣英雄人物模型。<br />\n<br />\n柯震東的家就住在父母家的樓上，其兄柯家洋早前置業搬離上址，他就獨佔連天台的特色單位，單是玄關位就可以容納40人，就連脫鞋坐的椅子也是一座老馬鞍，但豪宅看起來像Showroom，連飯桌面也沒擺放任何東西，他自稱患有強迫症：「我家就是這麼乾淨」，不過當他打開放滿波鞋的雜物櫃時，卻發現波鞋亂擺一通，他並預告下集會公開睡房內貌。<br />\n<br />\n他在個人YouTube頻道上載的最新影片《柯震東東區千萬藝術宅！超美強迫症的家超像樣品屋》，柯震東自稱居所是千萬藝術宅，雖然沒有透露豪宅價錢及面積，但查閱附近物業的成交價，都要1.3億台幣（約3,200萬港元）。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ljY899vC09BsRX61wAguLn4B-50=/1738x1011/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QPJ43NUGDRDSFJ6LPEGF3BNT5Y.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FljY899vC09BsRX61wAguLn4B-50%3D%2F1738x1011%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQPJ43NUGDRDSFJ6LPEGF3BNT5Y.JPG&h=03fbf017&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n玄關位背後的藝術品是柯爸爸的設計。（YouTube截圖）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/DwoXoudFkLObb9TtO3RquoA6Yfk=/1515x849/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/M7HVBBZ3GZEFDMHVSNEUUDK3WA.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FDwoXoudFkLObb9TtO3RquoA6Yfk%3D%2F1515x849%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FM7HVBBZ3GZEFDMHVSNEUUDK3WA.JPG&h=49c304fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n私人影院。（YouTube截圖）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/bYg6QhFLP9EZW02EbR9qw_OP-xQ=/1777x775/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WMINCAEDKZCLHHXCANVJSIZAC4.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FbYg6QhFLP9EZW02EbR9qw_OP-xQ%3D%2F1777x775%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWMINCAEDKZCLHHXCANVJSIZAC4.JPG&h=32f1df7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n沿室簡約。（YouTube截圖）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/7ikIHA6KUASuhb51vpwLwKrtA7k=/659x378/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UQFORFVDXVCOFGON74YYLUUZGE.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F7ikIHA6KUASuhb51vpwLwKrtA7k%3D%2F659x378%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUQFORFVDXVCOFGON74YYLUUZGE.JPG&h=b3760edd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n珍藏玩具花費不菲。（IG圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/D-RUb_HS_2pXUxx5azjupjVBVEo=/780x960/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TIM43LXU25ASDPBTLL5YXWJ2RE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FD-RUb_HS_2pXUxx5azjupjVBVEo%3D%2F780x960%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTIM43LXU25ASDPBTLL5YXWJ2RE.jpg&h=0f37ae4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n柯震東一家四口。（FB圖片）"},{"pid":"7abe09b0d3d813d12a6a5c47e195deb3f1e6e9e6","tid":2312962,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T11:58:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201205/XXCBOVIICZGYJKGBGED7XZT33Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201205%2FXXCBOVIICZGYJKGBGED7XZT33Q%2F&d=y57o2ak4%2BKgx1hG4eir1w7e6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=4b8c3f6a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201205%2FXXCBOVIICZGYJKGBGED7XZT33Q%2F&h=d4b24a56\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201205/XXCBOVIICZGYJKGBGED7XZT33Q/</a>"},{"pid":"d2cd7a7c79367bcec429d6e6b097f96c9b708f74","tid":2312962,"uid":3302,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T11:58:54.000Z","msg":"ssr首抽"},{"pid":"f09307ed8c39faf95ace965cc3125e92e11ef82d","tid":2312962,"uid":124372,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T12:00:33.000Z","msg":"本來好有前途<br />\n變左失德偽人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fd1e1320b9faec8cba2939c2ff7954812159e5f","tid":2312962,"uid":212249,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"f09307ed8c39faf95ace965cc3125e92e11ef82d","tid":2312962,"uid":124372,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T12:00:33.000Z","msg":"本來好有前途<br />\n變左失德偽人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T12:01:51.000Z","msg":"真<br />\n靚仔演技又唔太差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d26fe4c3528f5a4e48120cba69a2df23cf05166e","tid":2312962,"uid":152244,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T12:03:13.000Z","msg":"本身以為佢普普通通家境，紅左又吸毒搞到前途無曬大獲啦。點知原來咁有錢，我視野果然太狹窄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img 